object.script:
gears = {{-1,false,false,true}, {0,false,false,false}, {0.16,false,false,false}, {0.22,false,true,false}, {0.31,false,false,true}, {0.4,false,true,true}, {0.5,true,false,false}, {0.68,true,true,false}, {0.9,true,false,true}, {1.2,true,true,true}}
startup, reverse = true, false timer = 0
function onTick() rpsE = input.getNumber(1)*0.9 rpsW = input.getNumber(2) ws = input.getNumber(3)
type = property.getNumber("Transmission type") top = property.getNumber("Top gear")+2 park = property.getBool("Default mode")
upPulse = input.getBool(1) and not up up = input.getBool(1) downPulse = input.getBool(2) and not down down = input.getBool(2)
if startup then if park then gr,mode = 2,0 else gr,mode = 3,1 end startup = false end
if type == 1 then
if upPulse then mode = math.min(mode+1,2) elseif downPulse then mode = math.max(mode-1,-1) end
gb4 = false if mode == -1 then gr,gb4 = 1,true elseif mode == 0 then gr = 2 elseif mode == 2 or rpsW <= rpsE*gears[3][1] then gr = 3 elseif rpsW > rpsE*gears[top][1] then gr = top else for i = 4,top do if rpsW > rpsE*gears[i-1][1] and rpsW <= rpsE*gears[i][1] then gr = i break end end end
indicator = mode
elseif type == 2 then
if upPulse then mode = math.min(mode+1,2) elseif downPulse then mode = math.max(mode-1,0) end
if mode == 0 then gr = 2 elseif mode == 2 or rpsW <= rpsE*gears[3][1] then gr = 3 elseif rpsW > rpsE*gears[top][1] then gr = top else for i = 4,top do if rpsW > rpsE*gears[i-1][1] and rpsW <= rpsE*gears[i][1] then gr = i break end end end
if math.abs(rpsW) < 0.2 then timer = math.min(timer+1,10) if timer >= 10 and ws < -0.5 then reverse = true elseif timer >= 10 and ws > 0.5 then reverse = false end else timer = 0 end
if reverse then gr, gb4 = 1, true else gb4 = false end
indicator = mode
else
if upPulse then gr = math.min(gr+1,top) elseif downPulse then gr = math.max(gr-1,1) end gb4 = gr == 1 mode = (gr == 2 and 0) or 1 indicator = gr-2
end
brake = mode == 0 clutch = brake or (mode == 2 and rpsW > rpsE*0.2)
gb1,gb2,gb3 = gears[gr][2],gears[gr][3],gears[gr][4]
output.setNumber(1,indicator) output.setBool(1,gb1) output.setBool(2,gb2) output.setBool(3,gb3) output.setBool(4,gb4) output.setBool(5,reverse) output.setBool(6,brake) output.setBool(7,clutch) end

s = self
min = 0 max = 1
mean = 0 tick = 1 tickmax = 10 ratios = {}
for i = 1,tickmax do ratios[i] = 0 end
function clamp(x,y,z) return math.min(math.max(x,y),z) end
function pid(p,i,d) return{p=p, i=i, d=d, error=0, diff=0, integral=0, run=function(s, sp, pv, min, max, maxI) local error,diff,out error = sp-pv diff = error-s.error out = error*s.p+s.integral+diff*s.d s.error = error s.diff = diff if out > min and out < max then s.integral = clamp(s.integral + error*s.i, min, maxI) end return clamp(error*s.p+s.integral+diff*s.d, min, max) end } end
pid1 = pid(0.02,0.004,0) pid2 = pid(0.1,0.004,0) pid3 = pid(0.3,0.002,0)
function onTick()
air = input.getNumber(1) fuel = input.getNumber(2) target = input.getNumber(4) rps = input.getNumber(5)
on = input.getBool(1)
afr = property.getNumber("Modular engine Air-to-Fuel ratio") boost = property.getNumber("Reduce if RPS overshoots")*0.1 premade = property.getBool("Engine type")
if on and rps > 2 then if premade then out = pid3:run(target, rps, min, max, boost) mult = 1 else if fuel > 0 then ratios[tick] = air/fuel else ratios[tick] = 0 end
tick = tick+1 if tick > tickmax then tick = 1 end
mean = 0 for i,ratio in ipairs(ratios) do mean = mean+ratio end mean = mean/tickmax
if mean > 0 then multdiff = pid1:run(afr, mean, -0.48, 0.05, 0.05) else multdiff = 0 end
out = pid2:run(target, rps, min, max, boost)
mult = 0.52-multdiff end else out = 0 mult = 0 tick = 1 end
output.setNumber(1, out*mult) output.setNumber(2, out)
end

object.script:
-- Central Controller Microcontroller Script
threshold = property.getNumber("Threshold") -- This is the threshold above which we will start to reduce power max_rpm = property.getNumber("Max RPM") -- This will be updated with the highest RPM that's been seen smallestClutch = 0.5 avg_rpm = 0 power1 = 0 power2 = 0 power3 = 0 power4 = 0 function interpolation(start, finish, perc) return start + ((finish - start) * perc) end
function onTick() toggle = input.getBool(1) if not toggle then output.setNumber(1, 1) output.setNumber(2, 1) output.setNumber(3, 1) output.setNumber(4, 1) return end
-- Get the current RPM of each wheel local rpm1 = input.getNumber(1) local rpm2 = input.getNumber(2) local rpm3 = input.getNumber(3) local rpm4 = input.getNumber(4)
-- Update max_rpm if any of the current RPMs is higher max_rpm = math.max(max_rpm, rpm1, rpm2, rpm3, rpm4) currentMaxRpm = math.max(rpm1, rpm2, rpm3, rpm4) currentMinRpm = math.min(rpm1, rpm2, rpm3, rpm4) -- Calculate the average RPM of all wheels avg_rpm = (rpm1 + rpm2 + rpm3 + rpm4) / 4 temp1 = currentMaxRpm - avg_rpm temp2 = avg_rpm - currentMinRpm
biggestDiff = 0 if temp1 > temp2 then biggestDiff = temp1 else biggestDiff = temp2 end
-- Set the power to each wheel based on its RPM compared to the average RPM power1 = interpolation(0.5, 1, ((avg_rpm - rpm1) / biggestDiff)) power2 = interpolation(0.5, 1, ((avg_rpm - rpm2) / biggestDiff)) power3 = interpolation(0.5, 1, ((avg_rpm - rpm3) / biggestDiff)) power4 = interpolation(0.5, 1, ((avg_rpm - rpm4) / biggestDiff))
-- Output the power to each wheel's clutch using composite number write nodes output.setNumber(1, power1) output.setNumber(2, power2) output.setNumber(3, power3) output.setNumber(4, power4) end
function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() h = screen.getHeight() screen.setColor(255, 255, 255)
screen.drawText(0, 0, power1) screen.drawText(0, 6, power2) screen.drawText(0, 12, power3) screen.drawText(0, 18, power4)
screen.drawText(0, 24, "Avg. " .. avg_rpm) screen.drawText(0, 30, "Max " .. max_rpm) end

function onTick() w = input.getNumber(1) h = input.getNumber(2)
zoom = input.getNumber(7) x = input.getNumber(8) y = input.getNumber(9) bearing = input.getNumber(10) end
function onDraw()
w = screen.getWidth() h = screen.getHeight()
if (w<h) then size = w * 0.04 else size = h * 0.04 end
screen.drawMap(x, y, zoom)
screen.setColor(200, 0, 0, 128) drawCurrentPosition(w, h)
screen.setColor(220, 0, 0, 255) screen.drawRectF(findRectCenterX(w, 2), findRectCenterY(h, 2), 2, 2) end
function drawCurrentPosition(w, h) if (w<h) then radius = w * 0.09 else radius = h * 0.09 end cx = w/2 cy = h/2 compassDegrees = bearing * -360 % 360 translatedBearing = compassDegrees + 90 rad1 = math.rad(translatedBearing) rad2 = math.rad(translatedBearing + 140) rad3 = math.rad(translatedBearing + 220) x1 = cx - radius * math.cos(rad1) y1 = cy - radius * math.sin(rad1) x2 = cx - radius * math.cos(rad2) y2 = cy - radius * math.sin(rad2) x3 = cx - radius * math.cos(rad3) y3 = cy - radius * math.sin(rad3) screen.drawTriangleF(x1, y1, x2, y2, x3, y3) end
function findRectCenterX(w, rectW) return w/2 - (rectW / 2) end
function findRectCenterY(h, rectH) return h/2 - (rectH / 2) end
function cramp(min, max, value) if (value < min) then return min elseif (value > max) then return max else return value end end

function start()
dl(60,26,60.25,29.25) dl(59,25,61.25,25.25) dl(57,28,57.25,29.25) dl(56,27,56.25,27.25) dl(57,26,57.25,26.25) dl(56,25,56.25,25.25) dl(55,25,55.25,29.25) dl(53,26,53.25,29.25) dl(52,25,52.25,25.25) dl(51,26,51.25,29.25) dl(52,27,52.25,27.25) dl(47,25,49.25,25.25) dl(48,26,48.25,29.25) dl(44,25,45.25,25.25) dl(43,26,45.25,28.25) dl(43,29,44.25,29.25) end
function onTick() fuel = input.getNumber(1) -- please don't modify the Lua script if you reupload in a creation starter = input.getBool(1) blink = input.getBool(2) throt = input.getNumber(2) tempin = input.getNumber(3) eng = input.getNumber(4) conin = input.getNumber(5) conunit = property.getNumber("Fuel Consumption Units") inffuel = property.getBool("Infinite Fuel")
if conunit == 0 then con = conin constate = "L/s" elseif conunit == 1 then con = conin*60 constate = "L/m" elseif conunit == 2 then con = (conin/3.785) constate = "G/s" elseif conunit == 3 then con = (conin/3.785)*60 constate = "G/m" end
tenths = math.floor((con*10)%10) ones = math.floor(con%10) tens = math.floor((con/10)% 10) cap = property.getNumber("Maximum Fuel Capacity (L)") ftemp = property.getBool("Temperature Unit") rpm = property.getBool("Revolutions Unit") overheattemp = property.getNumber("Engine Overheat Warning Temperature") lowfuel = property.getNumber("Low Fuel Warning (%)")
if rpm then runit="RPM" rps = eng*60 else rps = eng runit="RPS" end
if ftemp then tunit="F" temp=(tempin*1.8)+32 else tunit="C" temp=tempin end
end
function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() h = screen.getHeight() sc(7, 7, 7)--background screen.drawClear() sc(31,40,17)--outline dr(1,1,w-3,7) dr(1,10,w-25,h-12) dr(42,10,20,13) sc(51,60,32)--fill drf(2,2,w-3,7) drf(2,11,w-25,h-12) drf(43,11,20,13) sc(42,53,25)--textbackground drf(4,3,w-6,5)--header drf(3,12,14,5)--rps drf(21,12,19,5) drf(3,18,18,5)--temp drf(22,18,18,5) --if ftemp==true then -- drf(22,18,4,5) --end drf(3,24,19,5)--fuel drf(26,24,14,5) drf(44,12,18,5)--fuel use drf(44,18,18,5) if starter == true then sc(100,100,20) drf(42,24,21,7) sc(4,4,4) start() else
if con > 0 and rps > 0 then
sc(20,100,20) drf(42,24,21,7) sc(4,4,4) tb(42,24,21,7,"RUN",0,0) else
if inffuel == true and throt > 0 and rps > 0 then
sc(20,100,20) drf(42,24,21,7) sc(4,4,4) tb(42,24,21,7,"RUN",0,0) end sc(100,20,20) drf(42,24,21,7) sc(4,4,4) tb(42,24,21,7,"OFF",0,0)
end end if (fuel/cap*100) < lowfuel and blink then sc(100,20,20) drf(3,24,37,5) end
sc(4,4,4)--text color dt(3,3,"eng") dt(17,3,"i") dt(20,3,"ne") dt(35,3,"st") dt(44,3,"at") dt(53,3,"us")
--tb(1,3,w,5,"engine stats",0,0) tb(3,12,20,5,runit,-1,0) tb(3,12,37,5,string.format("%.0f",rps),1,0) if temp < overheattemp then dt(3,18,"T") dt(7,18,"EMP") if ftemp then tb(3,18,33,5,string.format("%.0f",temp),1,0) dl(37,18,37,23) dl(38,18,40,18) dl(38,20,40,20) else tb(3,18,37,5,string.format("%.0fC",temp),1,0) end
else if blink then sc(100,20,20) else sc(42,53,25) end drf(3,18,37,5) sc(4,4,4) dt(3,18,"ov") dt(12,18,"erheat")
--tb(3,18,37,5,"TOO HOT",0,0)
end tb(3,24,20,5,"FUEL",-1,0) if (fuel/cap*100) > 99 then tb(3,24,37,5,"MAX",1,0) else tb(3,24,37,5,string.format("%.0f%%",(fuel/cap*100)),1,0) end tb(45,12,5,5,tens,0,0) tb(50,12,5,5,ones,0,0) tb(54,12,4,5,".",0,0) tb(57,12,5,5,tenths,0,0) tb(44,18,18,5,constate,0,0)
end

object.script:
--Check description for details...
--Color 1. Used for static color or as color of minimum value r1,g1,b1 = 250,10,10
--Color 2. Used as color of maximum value r2,g2,b2 = 10,250,10
--Color of unfilled part r3,g3,b3 = 250,250,250
--Text color r4,g4,b4 = 250,250,250
--Background color r5,g5,b5 = 0,0,0
max = property.getNumber('Max value') min = property.getNumber('Min value') dec = property.getNumber('Digits after decimal point') cm = property.getNumber('Color mode') os = property.getNumber('Text position offset (horizontal)') p1 = math.pi / 180
function rd(num) if dec > 0 then local mult = 10^(dec or 0) return math.floor(num * mult + 0.5) / mult else return math.floor(num) end end
function clamp(value,bot,top) if bot > top then bot, top = top, bot end if value < top and value > bot then return value elseif value > top then return top else return bot end end
function onTick() d = (max-min) val = rd(input.getNumber(1)) a = (val-min / d * 260 - 220) * p1 x = math.cos(a) * 14 + 16 y = math.sin(a) * 14 + 17 end
function onDraw() --backround screen.setColor(r5,g5,b5) screen.drawRectF(0, 0, 33, 33) screen.drawCircleF(16, 16, 9)
--text screen.setColor(r4,g4,b4) screen.drawTextBox(5,14,22,6,val,0,0)
val = val - min screen.setColor(r1,g1,b1) for i = -270, 90 do ang = i * (p1) if i > (val / d * 260) - 220 then screen.setColor(r3,g3,b3) else if cm == 0 then --modes screen.setColor(r1,g1,b1) elseif cm == 1 then h = d + d*0.01 screen.setColor(clamp(r1+(r2-r1)*((val)/h),r1,r2), clamp(g1+(g2-g1)*((val)/h),g1,g2), clamp(b1+(b2-b1)*((val)/h),b1,b2)) else screen.setColor(r1+(r2-r1)*((215+i)/255),g1+(g2-g1)*((215+i)/255),b1+(b2-b1)*((215+i)/255)) end end xc = math.cos(ang) * 14 + 16 yc = math.sin(ang) * 14 + 17 screen.drawCircleF(xc, yc, 1) end screen.setColor(r5,g5,b5) screen.drawRectF(0, 26, 33, 33) screen.setColor(r4,g4,b4) screen.drawTextBox(os, 26, 32, 6, property.getText('Text'), 0, 0) end
